reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great little cabinet
reviews.reviewText: This is exactly as described. It fits in my bathroom between the toilet and sink perfectly. It's sturdy and was easy to assemble. The drawers are fabric, so they fit odd shaped stuff as well. it holds all my daughters hair irons & curlers and flatteners, etc. Great cabinet!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars SO EASY TO USE
reviews.reviewText: I'm handicapped and can't walk easily. I set this up next to my couch and put my medications and items I use frequently in it. It's perfect. Also the top is study enough to hold my laptop. I open and close the drawers a few times each day and they're holding up very well. I don't see any negatives in this product. It's my whole little "world" right here at my fingertips. Highly recommend; definitely worth the money.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Very nice dresser with a neat design-easy assembly.
reviews.reviewText: I have the black version of this item and use it daily. I ordered this one for my bedroom and while its the same design as the first the lighter color fabric has an odor while the black one I have does not. I am taking one star away for that reason. Maybe it was just that particular unit I received. I sent it back but will likely try again. I use the other one I have to store all my digital drives and tech related supplies. Its study enough to hold a small lamp. You have to be a little careful rolling on carpet but overall it works great for a basic storage unit. Note that the drawers are fabric so not as robust as a wooden dresser so you have to treat them carefully. They simply pull directly in and out.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Wonderful 2 Drawer Cabinet
reviews.reviewText: This cute little drawer/cabinet can be put together in 20 minutes. It was exactly what I was looking for. 100% sturdy. Looks great. Great value for the money. Would recommend to others.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Easy to assemble and holds more than you think. I used this to store my yarn and DVDs. They fit will. One bin can hold four medium weight skeins (fyi) and I put my school binders on top :)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Missing a drawer bottom
reviews.reviewText: Decent quality cart. Fairly easy to assemble. But one of the drawer bottoms was missing from the box, and the drawer collapses without it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Lots of storage /reasonable price!
reviews.reviewText: I ordered this because I had a similar one in the past and it was very good. The metal frame and the wood top makes it very stable.The fabric drawers make it light so it moves easily (they work very well and are quite strong!). A good buy and I can reach the phone, TV control, pen and notepad without having to hunt for them somewhere in the sofa!
